'''''Breathe My Jets''''' was the vessel of [[Uran Lavint]]. It had enough cargo space to fit several [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300 light freighters]] in its cargo hold. The ship was captured by the [[Anakin Solo (starship)|''Anakin Solo'']] after Uran sold out her fellow [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] to the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]]. She intended to leave with her ship, but [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] stuck her with [[Duracrud|another]].

